manifest.name: Note Content Pusher
manifest.description: An Obsidian plugin to automatically create notes with some specified content when you link to a note that doesn't yet exist.
manifest.author: Henry Gustafson

data.manifestValue: An Obsidian plugin to automatically create notes with some specified content when you link to a note that doesn't yet exist.
data.communityListValue: Prepend or append specified content to a note (existing or new) without opening another pane.
